{"tid":2084874,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王祖藍抖音直播賣59蚊洗衣粉　七情上面手洗白恤衫！","createTime":"2020-06-29T13:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T15:04:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a92d6efb69c33d5411f9c2550be57b59700fc843","tid":2084874,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"抖音除了看到不少有趣片段之外，其實對不少香港藝人來說是無限商機，不需要天皇巨星，只要你有點知名度，,就有商品找你「帶貨」(直播賣商品),據知市價一個鐘幾萬人仔,之後還有分紅，足不出戶，不用受氣，好過去電視台拍劇走埠登台。<br />\n<br />\n當中港星以王祖藍最吃香,他在內地知名度高，憑內地綜藝《奔跑吧》紅遍全國，絶對是一綫港星，最近一年疫情影響下專注發展抖音市場，早前端午節晚上他就在抖音直播帶貨，賣的東西相當貼地，市價9元的英語課程，還有洗衣粉，雖然抖音直播規模不能跟內地大騷比較，但王祖藍依然賣力，賣洗衣粉時更親自用手洗，洗到七情上面，亦用標準國語力sell「59元你能賣16枝，哎呀...真的超利害，你不相信嗎?」網民見到王祖藍訓身推售,亦被打動，不少人留言表示購買。<br />\n<br />\n點擊睇王祖藍帶貨表情包"},{"pid":"9b4bfc1aa23a5d1b01b2f1ca4c605761c44b1cba","tid":2084874,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200629/354236577028902912.jpeg/iLjjiUqQDZsbySgdn13EJtWTBHu0pEtjzZONsM2TjbA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200629%2F354236577028902912.jpeg%2FiLjjiUqQDZsbySgdn13EJtWTBHu0pEtjzZONsM2TjbA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3bb60a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200629/354238629255712768.jpeg/RtxDSuAIEh3mLsR1wGOIYT8tKC99pzcDu7F0BbuxdAU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200629%2F354238629255712768.jpeg%2FRtxDSuAIEh3mLsR1wGOIYT8tKC99pzcDu7F0BbuxdAU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6274de8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小丑師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a9a9877c69061dcf1ab4321e3b321f5f777e3e","tid":2084874,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/im